        <h2><strong>Digital Media Syndication</strong><br/></h2>
        <strong>Health Content for Websites, Apps, and Social Media</strong></p>

        <p>
            We have created an easy way for public health partners to access our federally produced digital resources --&nbsp;
            including web content, images, video, data, infographics, and more &ndash; for use on in their website, apps,
        and social media. Syndication allows our science-based resources to be combined with information at state and
        local levels, and helps coordinate health messaging for maximum impact.</p>

